  <body>
    <sec>
      <title>Results</title>
      <p>Across the 24-week trial, metformin reduced fasting glucose in adults with prediabetes. The effect was significant relative to placebo.</p>
    </sec>
    <sec>
      <title>Discussion</title>
      <p>These findings indicate that metformin reduced fasting glucose consistently across subgroups.</p>
    </sec>
